one of the best shows ever ! bewitched is one of the best shows ever . forty years later their still fun to watch . each ep . is funny and well written . samantha marries the mortal darren and promises to give up her magic to the endless dismay of her mother the wonderful endora but luckily somehow samantha ends up using magic . aunt clara pops in often and creates her own chaos with her mix-up spells . every single ep . is my favorite .